data.meta_description:
280 likes, 3 comments - pleasedontquiz on April 16, 2024: "20 years ago on April 16, 2004 Kill Bill: Volume 2 was released in theaters. Written and directed by Quentin Tarantino, the film stars Uma Thurman, David Carradine, Michael Madsen, Daryl Hannah, and Gordon Liu. The DVD  of Kill Bill: Volume 1 was released three days before the theatrical release of the second film.
